#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.166"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.166:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.166:0.2"
msgid "17. Paṭipadāvagga "
msgstr "17. Practice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: chaṭṭhapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.166:0.3"
msgid "166. Ubhayasutta "
msgstr "166. Both "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.154, sc1
msgctxt "an4.166:1.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, paṭipadā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are four ways of practice. "

msgctxt "an4.166:1.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.166:1.3"
msgid "Dukkhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, dukkhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā dandhābhiññā, sukhā paṭipadā khippābhiññā. "
msgstr "~Painful practice with slow insight, ~painful practice with swift insight, ~pleasant practice with slow insight, and ~pleasant practice with swift insight. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.166:2.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yāyaṃ paṭipadā dukkhā dandhābhiññā, ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā ubhayeneva hīnā akkhāyati. Yampāyaṃ paṭipadā dukkhā, imināpāyaṃ hīnā akkhāyati; yampāyaṃ paṭipadā dandhā, imināpāyaṃ hīnā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "Of these, the painful practice with slow insight is said to be inferior in both ways: because it’s painful and because it’s slow. "

msgctxt "an4.166:2.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā ubhayeneva hīnā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "This practice is said to be inferior in both ways. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.166:3.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yāyaṃ paṭipadā dukkhā khippābhiññā, ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā dukkhattā hīnā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "The painful practice with swift insight is said to be inferior because it’s painful. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.166:4.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yāyaṃ paṭipadā sukhā dandhābhiññā, ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā dandhattā hīnā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "The pleasant practice with slow insight is said to be inferior because it’s slow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.166:5.1"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yāyaṃ paṭipadā sukhā khippābhiññā, ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā ubhayeneva paṇītā akkhāyati. Yampāyaṃ paṭipadā sukhā, imināpāyaṃ paṇītā akkhāyati; yampāyaṃ paṭipadā khippā, imināpāyaṃ paṇītā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "The pleasant practice with swift insight is said to be superior in both ways: because it’s pleasant, and because it’s swift. "

msgctxt "an4.166:5.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭipadā ubhayeneva paṇītā akkhāyati. "
msgstr "This practice is said to be superior in both ways. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.166:5.3"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, catasso paṭipadā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four ways of practice.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.166:5.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

